title "Outliers for HR Based on 2 Standard Deviations";
data _null_;
   file print;
   set remnull_Ban110;
   ***bring in the means and standard deviations;
   if _n_ = 1 then set Mean_Std;
   if price lt price_Mean - 2*price_StdDev and not missing(price)
      or price gt price_Mean + 2*price_StdDev then put ID= price=;
run;

In [39]:
title "Removing Outliers for HR Based on 2 Standard Deviations";
data remove_outliersBan110;
   file print;
   set remnull_Ban110;
   ***bring in the means and standard deviations;
   if _n_ = 1 then set Mean_Std;
   if price lt price_Mean - 2*price_StdDev and not missing(price)
      or price gt price_Mean + 2*price_StdDev then delete;
run;
